name: Tender Dreams #4 - People & Plants
description:
Tender Dreams is the 4th work in the series People & Plants.
It's a rather personal work in nature. 
The artwork deals with the concepts of love and letting go. The Raidho rune on the stone symbolizes the journey is the destination. Surrounded by a blooming variety of tender flowers the main figure is in the process of acceptance.
This is a high quality png file in 2500x3000px, 300dpi.
